# These are SERVER-SIDE secrets — set them in Cloudflare Pages → Settings → Environment variables.
# Do NOT put them in a .env file that gets committed or shipped to the browser.
#
# BEEHIIV_API_KEY          — from Beehiiv dashboard → Settings → API (secret, write scope: subscriptions)
# BEEHIIV_PUBLICATION_ID   — from Beehiiv dashboard → Settings → Publication (plain text)
#
# Example (Cloudflare Pages dashboard, not a .env file):
#   BEEHIIV_API_KEY         = sk_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
#   BEEHIIV_PUBLICATION_ID  = pub_xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
#
# The app builds and runs fine without these — email capture silently no-ops,
# PDF generation still works.
